 === 6) Arm unified 1R stop via reusable ‾E2‾80‾9CS
et Auto Stop‾E2‾80‾9D script ===‾0D‾0Aif ($useAutoS
top == "Yes") {‾0D‾0A    ExecHotKey("Set Auto Stop"
);   ‾0D‾0A}‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// == 7) Build and set take
