ert and abort unless we are adding to an existing p
osition‾0D‾0Aif (($stopVsBidFail == 1 || $spreadToo
Wide == 1) && $posBefore <=0) {‾0D‾0A    $msg = "Sp
read/Stop safety failed for " + Symbol + "¥n" +‾0D‾0A
