e; then fallback to SL‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// 3) Cancel exis
ting SELL-side working orders‾0D‾0A$accObj = GetAcc
ountObj($myAcc);‾0D‾0A$accObj.CancelOrder("SELL", $
mySym, 0);‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// Let cancels register; avoi
