Ms);‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A// =====================‾0D‾0A// 8)
 NOT YET IN PROFIT ‾E2‾86‾92 BE LIMIT SELL‾0D‾0A// 
=====================‾0D‾0Aif ($bid < $beStopTrigge
r) {‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A    // ARCAL uses penny ticks‾0D‾0A
    $incBE = 0.01;‾0D‾0A‾0D‾0A    $px = Round($avgS
